| Nominal tread radius \(t\) | 0.1 | m |
| Load \(F\) | 5000 | N |
| Contact width \(w\) | 0.2 | m |
| Initial pressure \(P_0\) | 2.5 MPa | Pa |
| Temperature \(T\) | 293 K | K |

