\[
d_0 = \frac{F}{P_0\,w} = \frac{5000}{2.5\times10^6 \times 0.2} \approx 0.01\;\text{m} \;(1\;\text{cm}).
\]

Effective radius:

\[
R_{\text{eff},0} = R_0 + t - d_0 = 0.3 + 0.1 - 0.01 = 0.39\;\text{m}.
\]

